  "root_text": {
    "iti60:0.1": "Itivuttaka 60 ",
    "iti60:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti60:0.3": "Dutiyavagga ",
    "iti60:0.4": "Puññakiriyavatthusutta ",
    "iti60:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti60:2.1": "“Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, puññakiriyavatthūni. ",
    "iti60:2.2": "Katamāni tīṇi? ",
    "iti60:2.3": "Dānamayaṁ puññakiriyavatthu, sīlamayaṁ puññakiriyavatthu, bhāvanāmayaṁ puññakiriyavatthu—",
    "iti60:2.4": "imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi puññakiriyavatthūnī”ti. ",
    "iti60:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti60:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti60:3.1": "“Puññameva so sikkheyya, ",
    "iti60:3.2": "āyataggaṁ sukhudrayaṁ; ",
    "iti60:3.3": "Dānañca samacariyañca, ",
    "iti60:3.4": "mettacittañca bhāvaye. ",
    "iti60:4.1": "Ete dhamme bhāvayitvā, ",
    "iti60:4.2": "tayo sukhasamuddaye; ",
    "iti60:4.3": "Abyābajjhaṁ sukhaṁ lokaṁ, ",
    "iti60:4.4": "paṇḍito upapajjatī”ti. ",
    "iti60:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti60:5.2": "Paṭhamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti60:0.1": "So It Was Said 60 ",
    "iti60:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti60:0.3": "Chapter Two ",
    "iti60:0.4": "Grounds for Making Merit ",
    "iti60:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti60:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three grounds for making merit. ",
    "iti60:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti60:2.3": "Giving, ethical conduct, and meditation are all grounds for making merit. ",
    "iti60:2.4": "These are the three grounds for making merit.” ",
    "iti60:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti60:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti60:3.1": "“One should practice only good deeds, ",
    "iti60:3.2": "whose happy outcome stretches ahead. ",
    "iti60:3.3": "Giving and moral conduct, ",
    "iti60:3.4": "developing a mind of love: ",
    "iti60:4.1": "having developed these ",
    "iti60:4.2": "three things yielding happiness, ",
    "iti60:4.3": "that astute one is reborn ",
    "iti60:4.4": "in a happy, pleasing world.” ",
    "iti60:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "iti60:4.3": "Abyābajjhaṁ → abyāpajjaṁ (an6.37:1 [37. Chaḷaṅgadānasutta]; iti22:1 [Mettasutta]) "
  },
